Information
------------------------------

Daily Planet: 2016 Future Tech Week CES Edition
Discovery Channel's flagship science magazine with hosts Ziya Tong and Dan Riskin continues to explore the latest science behind the headlines and the coolest scientific developments that impact our lives in every way. Daily Planet ushers in 2016 by keeping pace with the technology trends to come with "Future Tech Week", 
We kick off the year in a big way with the very latest in tech across the world. Our hosts are on-location at the annual Consumer Electronics Show (CES) to show us what 2016 has in store.
